cat("Hello my alien friend! We are carbon-based lives on a planet called the Earth, from a distant galaxy called the solar system. Who are you? Where are you from? It seems that you have the intent to occupy some habitable-zone, Earth-like exoplanets. We kindly request you not to do that, because we are running out of resources here on Earth, and every Earth-like planet is invaluable for us. Thank you!")
